    <string name="onboarding_caveats_title">Before you start</string>
    <string name="onboarding_caveat_support_title">Support grows device by device</string>
    <string name="onboarding_caveat_support_body">Charge control is added one phone at a time, so not every device is supported yet. Amply shows where yours stands and, when it can, how to help add support.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_caveat_setup_title">One-time setup on supported devices</string>
    <string name="onboarding_caveat_setup_body">To change the charge policy, Amply needs elevated access granted once — either by running a command from a computer over ADB, or on-device with Shizuku. If your device is supported, the dashboard walks you through it.</string>

